OL,7,FShoppers have benefited from retailers
OL,8,Fcutting prices this month in a bid to
OL,9,Frevive consumer demand, new figures
OL,10,Fshow.
OL,12,FThe rate that prices are rising in
OL,13,Fshops across the country has returned
OL,14,Fto "normal" levels, according to an
OL,15,Finfluential retail group.
OL,17,FShop prices in May were 0.6% higher
OL,18,Fthan a year earlier, the lowest growth
OL,19,Fsince November 2021, the British
OL,20,FRetail Consortium (BRC)-NielsenIQ Shop
OL,21,FPrice Index found.
