OL,5,Cdemand
OL,7,FThe figure is down from 0.8% in April
OL,8,Fand below the three-month average rate
OL,9,Fof 0.9%.
OL,11,FThe survey period covered the first
OL,12,Fweek of May.
OL,14,FIt means that overall prices are still
OL,15,Frising in shops ` which include
OL,16,Fsupermarkets, department stores, and
OL,17,Ffashion chains ` but not as steeply as
OL,18,Fthey have been.
OL,20,FBut some items have seen prices fall
OL,21,Fcompared with the previous year.
