OL,7,FThe BRC said this was especially the
OL,8,Fcase for sugary products which had
OL,9,Ffelt the effects of higher global
OL,10,Fsugar prices.
OL,12,FMike Watkins, head of retailer and
OL,13,Fbusiness insight for NielsenIQ, said:
OL,14,F"Across the industry, whilst
OL,15,Finflationary pressure has eased and
OL,16,Fthere is some improvement in shopper
OL,17,Fsentiment, the unseasonable weather
OL,18,Fhas dampened retail sales so lower
OL,19,Fprices look set to continue and
OL,20,Fpromotional activity is likely to
OL,21,Fdrive demand."
